              "content": "                                                               Table \"auth.deep_link\"\n         Column         |           Type           | Collation | Nullable |      Default      | Storage  | Compression | Stats target | Description \n------------------------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+-------------------+----------+-------------+--------------+-------------\n id                     | uuid                     |           | not null | gen_random_uuid() | plain    |             |              | \n subject_urn            | text                     |           | not null |                   | extended |             |              | \n subject_label          | text                     |           |          |                   | extended |             |              | \n target_tenant_id       | uuid                     |           | not null |                   | plain    |             |              | \n created_by_resident_id | uuid                     |           | not null |                   | plain    |             |              | \n expires_at             | timestamp with time zone |           | not null |                   | plain    |             |              | \n revoked_at             | timestamp with time zone |           |          |                   | plain    |             |              | \n created_at             | timestamp with time zone |           | not null | now()             | plain    |             |              | \nIndexes:\n    \"deep_link_pkey\" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)\n    \"deep_link_target_tenant_id_idx\" btree (target_tenant_id)\nForeign-key constraints:\n    \"deep_link_created_by_resident_id_fkey\" FOREIGN KEY (created_by_resident_id) REFERENCES app.resident(id)\n    \"deep_link_target_tenant_id_fkey\" FOREIGN KEY (target_tenant_id) REFERENCES app.tenant(id)\nReferenced by:\n    TABLE \"auth.otp_login\" CONSTRAINT \"otp_login_deep_link_id_fkey\" FOREIGN KEY (deep_link_id) REFERENCES auth.deep_link(id) ON DELETE CASCADE\nPolicies (row security enabled): (none)\nAccess method: heap\n\n"
